                        <interp inst="t18440408-name-636" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE RICHARDS</persName>
                  </hi>. I went to bed between eleven and twelve o'clock in the evening—I saw nothing of these clothes.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18440408-name-637" type="witnessName">
